597
00:39:52,710 --> 00:39:54,380
Sit down, come on!

598
00:39:54,880 --> 00:39:57,550
- It's dark in here.
- Now don't fall asleep!

599
00:39:59,360 --> 00:40:01,520
We'll bet that -

600
00:40:01,590 --> 00:40:04,080
What's the time?

601
00:40:04,160 --> 00:40:06,030
Twenty to 9:00.

602
00:40:06,100 --> 00:40:08,930
That in, let's say, 12 hours...

603
00:40:09,000 --> 00:40:10,800
all three of you'll be kaput.

604
00:40:15,010 --> 00:40:16,240
What?

605
00:40:17,910 --> 00:40:19,930
You bet us, that tomorrow at 9:00,
