619
00:41:07,570 --> 00:41:09,230
Help yourselves and get out.

620
00:41:11,570 --> 00:41:15,230
Don't you think Fred and Eva
might come and see what's going on?

621
00:41:15,310 --> 00:41:17,900
And give us a good hiding, right?

622
00:41:22,980 --> 00:41:24,140
Okay.

623
00:41:24,220 --> 00:41:25,710
As they say on TV:

624
00:41:25,790 --> 00:41:27,450
The bets are placed!

625
00:41:29,120 --> 00:41:31,460
And what'll we do now?

626
00:41:31,530 --> 00:41:34,320
Could you kindly make us some food?

627
00:41:35,000 --> 00:41:36,660
You worry me, Fatty.

628
00:41:37,330 --> 00:41:39,560
Can't you control yourself?

629
00:41:40,240 --> 00:41:42,570
You've just gobbled up the sausage.

630
00:41:43,740 --> 00:41:45,230
It's disgusting.

631
00:41:45,310 --> 00:41:46,800
What are these people going to think?

632
00:41:46,880 --> 00:41:48,710
I haven't eaten since lunchtime!

633
00:41:48,780 --> 00:41:50,680
And stop calling me Fatty.

634
00:41:50,750 --> 00:41:52,870
- Okay, Tom.
- Okay, Jerry.

635
00:41:54,990 --> 00:41:57,320
But can't you pay some attention
to your appearance?

636
00:41:57,990 --> 00:42:00,320
You think it makes you more attractive?

637
