649
00:42:33,830 --> 00:42:35,230
What?

650
00:42:36,670 --> 00:42:39,030
Did you hear that, madam?

651
00:42:40,540 --> 00:42:42,200
That's really cheeky!

652
00:42:42,870 --> 00:42:45,240
We can't put up with that, can we?

653
00:42:53,850 --> 00:42:55,680
Hey you! Indian!

654
00:42:56,520 --> 00:42:58,180
What's your name anyway?

655
00:43:02,530 --> 00:43:03,960
Georg.

656
00:43:05,230 --> 00:43:06,720
Like Daddy.

657
00:43:06,800 --> 00:43:08,100
Lovely!

658
00:43:09,440 --> 00:43:11,770
Georgie-boy, come over to me.

659
00:43:13,340 --> 00:43:14,830
Come here.

660
00:43:20,150 --> 00:43:22,710
Come on. Sit down beside me.
We're going to play a game.

661
00:43:22,790 --> 00:43:23,770
Let the boy go!

662
00:43:25,150 --> 00:43:27,990
I know you don't want to play,
but you'll see, it's fun.

663
00:43:28,060 --> 00:43:29,720
Let the boy go!

664
00:43:31,700 --> 00:43:34,690
See how your mother's
standing up for you?

665
00:43:34,770 --> 00:43:37,700
- Dad could take an example from her!
- Stop it!

666
00:43:37,770 --> 00:43:40,430
