Kitten in the Bag.

669
00:43:50,350 --> 00:43:51,840
You'll see, it's fun.

670
00:43:54,850 --> 00:43:57,190
There! Don't panic! Nothing will happen.

671
00:43:57,290 --> 00:43:59,450
I said this is a nice game.

672
00:43:59,490 --> 00:44:00,980
A family game.

673
00:44:01,830 --> 00:44:04,960
Daddy is playing too
so he doesn't get bored.

674
00:44:05,030 --> 00:44:07,020
Right. Now listen!

675
00:44:07,700 --> 00:44:09,860
You'll have to keep still, or it's no fun.

676
00:44:11,210 --> 00:44:12,870
