Yes.

683
00:44:29,530 --> 00:44:31,220
Great. Then we can finally start.

684
00:44:31,900 --> 00:44:33,730
So, the starting point of our game

685
00:44:33,800 --> 00:44:37,960
was that mommy and our little Indian
wanted to slip out of here.

686
00:44:38,040 --> 00:44:40,010
- But why?
- Don't know.

687
00:44:40,070 --> 00:44:41,730
