With the boy here.

694
00:44:57,490 --> 00:44:59,320
That's why we play
"Kitten in the Bag. "

695
00:44:59,360 --> 00:45:01,300
To preserve moral decency.

696
00:45:01,360 --> 00:45:05,360
The kiddy wears a pillow case
