697
00:45:09,640 --> 00:45:12,130
We mustn't hurt the kitty cat, right?
Dad's broken leg is enough.

698
00:45:12,210 --> 00:45:14,040
Let the child go. Please!

699
00:45:14,110 --> 00:45:16,170
Exactly. Daddy's playing with us too.

700
00:45:21,820 --> 00:45:23,480
What are we waiting for?

701
00:45:26,490 --> 00:45:30,590
Tell your wife not to be so shy.
It's ridiculous.

702
00:45:30,660 --> 00:45:32,530
Anyway, I'm sure she isn't flabby.

703
00:45:34,200 --> 00:45:36,690
Please, let the child go.

704
00:45:37,540 --> 00:45:38,870
Please!

705
00:45:40,210 --> 00:45:42,730
