716
00:48:36,140 --> 00:48:37,970
Go and clean him up.

717
00:48:38,040 --> 00:48:40,700
- Let the child go!
- I won't do anything to him.

718
00:49:28,000 --> 00:49:29,660
Will you sit down, please?

719
