727
00:50:39,450 --> 00:50:41,110
Does it hurt a lot?

728
00:50:41,180 --> 00:50:42,840
Why don't you kill us right away?

729
00:50:43,520 --> 00:50:45,230
Don't forget the entertainment value.

730
00:50:45,230 --> 00:50:47,040
We'd all be deprived of our pleasure.

731
00:51:46,750 --> 00:51:48,980
Sorry about your leg.

732
00:51:49,060 --> 00:51:51,320
But it's your fault, if I might say so.

733
00:51:51,990 --> 00:51:53,830
Why did you smack Paul?

734
00:51:58,030 --> 00:52:01,030
For me, begging for the eggs
to no avail was very unpleasant.

735
00:52:02,210 --> 00:52:04,330
Humiliating, actually.

736
00:52:04,410 --> 00:52:06,070
I don't know if you realize that.

737
00:52:07,210 --> 00:52:09,540
It's just not worth it,

738
00:52:09,610 --> 00:52:12,100
all this charade, for a box of eggs.

739
00:52:15,890 --> 00:52:19,380
They should still be there.

740
00:52:19,460 --> 00:52:22,290
