754
00:53:21,060 --> 00:53:23,720
Nothing's happened yet!

755
00:53:25,230 --> 00:53:26,430
We'll say...

756
00:53:26,500 --> 00:53:29,530
that Georg broke his leg in the boat.

757
00:53:30,470 --> 00:53:32,800
- Everyone'll believe it, and -
- Please stop.

758
00:53:32,870 --> 00:53:34,540
Why are you humiliating yourself?

759
00:53:34,610 --> 00:53:36,670
It's just as unpleasant for me as for you.

760
00:54:14,470 --> 00:54:15,810
Georgie?

761
00:54:17,310 --> 00:54:18,800
Where are you?

762
00:55:44,330 --> 00:55:45,820
Georgie!

763
00:55:45,890 --> 00:55:47,380
I'm coming!

764
00:56:41,520 --> 00:56:43,690
Hold on,
I'll put on some music for us.

765
00:57:27,140 --> 00:57:29,080
Don't come any closer!

766
00:57:31,310 --> 00:57:33,040
The trigger!

767
00:57:35,050 --> 00:57:36,990
You have to prime the trigger!

768
00:57:53,840 --> 00:57:56,000
And you need to pull it too!

769
00:58:55,680 --> 00:58:57,840
Tralee trala, here we are!

770
00:58:59,180 --> 00:59:00,540
Mommy!

771
00:59:03,620 --> 00:59:05,210
Hello, my darling!

772
00:59:06,390 --> 00:59:08,410
Is everything okay?

773
00:59:12,530 --> 00:59:13,790
They've -

774
00:59:14,300 --> 00:59:16,730
